title: REGISTER_ARCHETYPES
content:
0x3C2F9037// RegisterArchetypes
void REGISTER_ARCHETYPES(func factory);Parameters:factory: A function returning a list of archetypes.Experimental: This native may be altered or removed in future versions of CitizenFX without warning.Registers a set of archetypes with the game engine. These should match CBaseArchetypeDef class information from the game.Examples:LuaRegisterArchetypes(function()
	return {
		{
			flags = 32,
			bbMin = vector3(-39.99570000, -8.00155600, -2.56818800),
			bbMax = vector3(40.00439000, 7.99858000, 1.44575100),
			bsCentre = vector3(0.00434110, -0.00148870, -0.56121830),
			bsRadius = 40.84160000,
			name = 'my_asset',
			textureDictionary = 'my_asset',
			physicsDictionary = 'my_asset',
			assetName = 'my_asset',
			assetType = 'ASSET_TYPE_DRAWABLE',
			lodDist = 450.45,
			specialAttribute = 0
		}
	}
end)
